vfs_both_paths.note: Both-spellings /tmp profile: requests to both /tmp/* and /private/tmp/* are allowed in this suite (control).

vfs_private_tmp_only.note: Canonical-only /private/tmp profile: requests to both /tmp/* and /private/tmp/* are allowed in this suite.

vfs_tmp_only.note: Alias-only /tmp profile: requests to both /tmp/* and /private/tmp/* are denied in this suite.
